
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Smart Library Management System</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{

background:
linear-gradient(
rgba(0,0,0,.75),
rgba(0,0,0,.75)
),

url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521587760476-6c12a4b040da?w=1800");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
background-attachment:fixed;

color:white;
}

/* NAVBAR */

nav{

display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;

padding:20px 60px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

position:sticky;
top:0;
}

.logo{

font-size:32px;
font-weight:bold;

color:#FFD700;
}

nav ul{

display:flex;
gap:30px;

list-style:none;
}

nav ul li{

cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

nav ul li:hover{

color:#FFD700;
}

.btn{

padding:12px 25px;

border:none;

border-radius:30px;

background:
linear-gradient(
45deg,
#FFD700,
#F5DEB3
);

font-weight:bold;

cursor:pointer;
}

/* HERO */

.hero{

height:90vh;

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;

justify-content:center;
align-items:center;

text-align:center;

padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{

font-size:75px;

margin-bottom:20px;

background:
linear-gradient(
90deg,
#fff,
#FFD700,
#fff
);

-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.hero p{

font-size:22px;

max-width:800px;

color:#F5E6C8;
}

/* SEARCH */

.search-box{

margin-top:35px;
}

.search-box input{

width:450px;

padding:15px;

border:none;

border-radius:30px;
}

.search-box button{

padding:15px 25px;

border:none;

border-radius:30px;

background:#FFD700;

font-weight:bold;

cursor:pointer;
}

/* STATS */

.stats{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:30px;

padding:40px;
}

.stat-card{

width:220px;

padding:25px;

text-align:center;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(12px);

border-radius:20px;
}

.stat-card h2{

color:#FFD700;
}

/* SECTION TITLE */

.section-title{

text-align:center;

font-size:40px;

color:#FFD700;

margin:50px 0;
}

/* CARDS */

.container{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:30px;

padding:20px 40px 60px;
}

.card{

width:300px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(15px);

border-radius:20px;

padding:25px;

transition:.4s;
}

.card:hover{

transform:translateY(-10px);

box-shadow:
0 15px 35px rgba(255,215,0,.3);
}

.card h3{

color:#FFD700;

margin-bottom:15px;
}

.card ul{

line-height:1.8;
}

/* LOGIN SECTION */

.form-section{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

padding:50px;
}

.form-box{

width:600px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(15px);

padding:30px;

border-radius:20px;
}

.form-box h2{

text-align:center;

margin-bottom:20px;

color:#FFD700;
}

input, select{

width:100%;

padding:12px;

margin:10px 0;

border:none;

border-radius:10px;
}

/* FOOTER */

footer{

text-align:center;

padding:25px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.4);

margin-top:30px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>

<div class="logo">📚 Smart Library</div>

<ul>

<li>Home</li>
<li>Books</li>
<li>Materials</li>
<li>Students</li>
<li>Contact</li>

</ul>

<button class="btn">Login</button>

</nav>

<section class="hero">

<h1>Smart Library Management</h1>

<p>

Search Books, Download Materials, Track Borrow History
and Manage Library Activities Easily.

</p>

<div class="search-box">

<input type="text"
placeholder="Search Books, Authors, Subjects...">

<button>Search</button>

</div>

</section>

<div class="stats">

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>15,000+</h2>
<p>Books Available</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>5,000+</h2>
<p>Students</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>800+</h2>
<p>Materials</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>98%</h2>
<p>Availability</p>
</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">
Library Features
</h2>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<h3>👨‍🎓 Student Portal</h3>

<ul>
<li>Register/Login</li>
<li>Search Books</li>
<li>Borrow History</li>
<li>Check Fine</li>
<li>Download Materials</li>
<li>My Profile</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>👨‍💼 Librarian Dashboard</h3>

<ul>
<li>Add Books</li>
<li>Update Books</li>
<li>Delete Books</li>
<li>Issue Books</li>
<li>Return Status</li>
<li>Fine Management</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>📄 Study Materials</h3>

<ul>
<li>Semester Wise Notes</li>
<li>Department Materials</li>
<li>PDF Downloads</li>
<li>Latest Uploads</li>
<li>Subject Resources</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>📚 Digital Catalog</h3>

<ul>
<li>Book Search</li>
<li>Author Search</li>
<li>Category Search</li>
<li>Availability Status</li>
<li>Issue Tracking</li>
</ul>

</div>

</div>

<div class="form-section">

<div class="form-box">

<h2>Student Login</h2>

<form>

<input type="text"
placeholder="Student ID">

<input type="password"
placeholder="Password">

<select>

<option>Select Department</option>

<option>CSE</option>
<option>IT</option>
<option>ECE</option>
<option>EEE</option>

</select>

<button class="btn"
style="width:100%; margin-top:10px;">

Login

</button>

</form>

</div>

</div>

<footer>

📚 Smart Library Management System © 2026

</footer>

</body>

</html>
